<p>Fairly quiet.  Rained hard this morning.</p>
<p>Sunday 26.11.16<br/>Fritz shelled heavily practically the whole day.  Relieved at 3 pm, arrived back at camp about 5 pm, where a mail was awaiting our return.  Roads in an awful state, mud up to our knees.</p>
<p>Monday 27.11.16<br/>Rested all day.  Sgt Thompson &amp; Sgt Roberts evacuated &amp; being only N.C.O. left in C. section was put in charge.  Wrote long letter home; issued with top boots.</p>
